# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore for vouchfx-telemetry-backend (.NET 8 service + Bicep IaC)
# Covers: .NET build output, IDEs, NuGet, test results, secrets, Docker/Testcontainers, OS cruft.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

## .NET build output
bin/
obj/
out/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
artifacts/
publish/
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
project.lock.json

## .NET tool / restore caches
.dotnet/
.packages/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/
packages/

## Test results & coverage
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coverletoutput
coverage*.json
coverage*.xml
coverage*.info
TestResults/

## Visual Studio / Rider / VS Code
.vs/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.code-workspace

## Roslyn / MSBuild
*.binlog
msbuild.log

## Local secrets & environment — NEVER commit a real ingest token or DB password
*.secrets
secrets.json
secrets.local.*
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
appsettings.*.local.json

## Bicep
*.bicepparam.local

## Testcontainers / Docker scratch
.testcontainers.properties

## OS-generated files
.DS_Store
._*
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

## Logs & temp
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
*~

## Agent / tooling scratch
.claude/
.serena/

## GitHub Pages build output (scripts/build_site.py)
_site/
